item.title: rbrito: change to .blog.setup on Rogério Brito's Digital Junkyard
item.dcterms:creator: rbrito
item.description:
Changed pages: .blog.setup
Changed by: rbrito
Commit type: git
Date: 00:10:13 2011-05-31
Add my setup to the sources of the site.
This way, I don't have to carry around the setup file separately from the
source of the whole site. As far as I am concerned, the setup of the site
*is* a source of the site and it should be kept with it, especially for
sites that are statically created (like this one).
I wish that Joey Hess allows this on future versions of ikiwiki.
